# Always regenerate presentation after YAML changes

Whenever `examples/how_to_come_out_of_testing_and_trials.yaml` is modified, **always regenerate** the PPTX in that same turn. Do not end the task without running the rebuild, including for tiny edits (highlights, spelling, emojis). From the repository root:

```bash
python -m praisonaippt.cli -i examples/how_to_come_out_of_testing_and_trials.yaml -o examples/how_to_come_out_of_testing_and_trials.pptx
```

Do this in the same turn as the edit (or immediately after), so `examples/how_to_come_out_of_testing_and_trials.pptx` stays in sync and Google Drive upload runs if `auto_upload_gdrive` is enabled in the YAML.
